<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4396834>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 9–14. Diamesa bertrami-type: 9—head capsule, A—mandible. Diamesa Tatra-type A: 10—head capsule, A—mandible. Diamesa Tatra-type A: 11—mentum (arrow indicates position of seta submenti). Diamesa Tatra-type B: 12—head capsule (arrows indicate mandible and genal setae). Diamesa Tatra-type B: 13—mentum (arrow indicates position of seta submenti). Pseudodiamesa branickii-type: 14—head capsule (arrow indicates antenna)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4396834/files/figure.png" .

